Feature: Custom Pages with Homepage Toggle

This plan tracks adding custom page support and the ability to toggle which page is the homepage.

## Objectives
- Backend endpoints for pages
- Frontend toggle for homepage selection
- Real-time broadcast of homepage updates
- Reconcile endpoint mismatch between spec and implementation

## Issues
- Drift: `backend_spec` lists `PUT /set-homepage` while implementation uses `POST /pages/{id}/set-homepage`. This needs reconciliation.
